                    User-Agent: ${userAgent}
                 </p>
              </div>

              <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #6B7280; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">Mensaje del cliente</p>
              <div style="background-color: #ffffff; border-left: 3px solid #006DE7; padding: 10px 20px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px;">
                ${message.replace(/\n/g, '<br>')}
              </div>

            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #F9FAFB; padding: 20px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #E5E7EB;">
